NG  August is here whether we are ready or not.\", \"from\": 4136, \"to\": 4192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is my least favorite month since it is always the hottest no matter where you live in the world.\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Surprisingly, the other night a few friends fromTifereth Israel Synagogue's Sisterhood met up at La Mesita Park in La Mesa.\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4351, \"end\": 4357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999946221578, \"rank\": 5.377829179839072e-09, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 4409, \"end\": 4416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_La_Mesa\", \"score\": 0.9999957738603542, \"rank\": 4.2261560514972314e-06, \"text\": \"La Mesa\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_La_Mesa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_La_Mesa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The weather was not too bad.\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Under the pavilion, and the shade of the many eucalyptus trees, it made the night pleasant visiting with friends and enjoying a nosh together.\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is good to stop, meet up with friends and enjoy the fresh air.\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When working and going about the daily tasks of life, it is nice to take a break and spend some time doing something out of the ordinary,\\u00a0 that is not on the daily check list of the day.\", \"from\": 4657, \"to\": 4843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"*  OBITUARY NOTICE  Penelope Kassarpassed away on Sunday, July 28.\", \"from\": 4845, \"to\": 4911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Funeral services were held on Wednesday, July 31 in Cincinnati.\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4964, \"end\": 4974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cincinnati\", \"score\": 0.9999999985984687, \"rank\": 1.1052737270597422e-09, \"text\": \"Cincinnati\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cincinnati\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cincinnati\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In lieu of flowers, memorial contributions may be made to Seacrest Village byclicking here.\", \"from\": 4976, \"to\": 5067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"*  Cailin Acostais the assistant editor of theSan Diego Jewish World.\", \"from\": 5069, \"to\": 5138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5072, \"end\": 5078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cailin_(song)\", \"score\": 0.9999999961182766, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cailin\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cailin_(song)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cailin_(song)\"}, {\"begin\": 5112, \"end\": 5118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thesan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"theSan\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thesan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thesan\"}, {\"begin\": 5119, \"end\": 5124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"score\": 0.9884684044940412, \"rank\": 0.011666124535363897, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego_Columbus\"}, {\"begin\": 5125, \"end\": 5131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.997501884462261, \"rank\": 0.002437196698446429, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PLEASE CLICK ON ANY AD BELOW 